  "description": {
   "en": "\"Bonobono\" has been evaluated as philosophical even though it is a four-panel manga since its release. So far, the postcards from our readers have been \"I cried\", \"Healed\", \"Cute\", \"Interesting\", \"Refreshing to read\", \"My heart was warmed\", and \"I got the essence\". There were many warm voices such as \"I think I will do my best\". This time, we have selected and published the works that we want you to read on \"the day you want to cry\" and the ones you want to read on the \"day you want to be healed\". \"Nakitai Hi\" includes a special interview with Etsuko Yakushimaru. In addition, Igara-san wrote a new poem for each volume. We hope that these gems of art that make your life easier will surely reach your heart!"
  },
